 in the basket rather than visible expenditure levels - so that visible
 expenditure is not subject to the endogeneity problem that arises due to
 total expenditure being on the right hand side and visible expenditure
 on left hand side of the equation
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "JaikumarConspConIneq"

\end_inset

