 the markets exist for the category).
 The availability of an item (all supply issues) are incorporated in 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

 as well.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Notice also that participation of consumers in the same market is key in
 the view of the status advantage through price differences.
 Certain items may have higher price varieties due to transport costs -
