\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Since the asset based model is not concerned with the differences in visibility
 of items within a functional category, the measurement of visibility index
 (as employed by Heffetz
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "heffetz_visibility"

\end_inset

